QuestData.Title: Eyes in the Overlook
QuestData.Description: Alliance personnel from the Skyfire were spotted parachuting into Blackbeak Overlook.$B$BI was unable to confirm numbers or positions during my flyover, but I did see parachutes tangled in treetops and a LOT of ravenbears on the ground.$B$BIf anyone is up there, they must be laying low and keeping an eye on us.$B$BI have posted a rider at the top of the overlook to keep watch while I press forward into Stormheim.$B$B- Liza Cullen, Dread-Rider - 1st Wing
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Cullen must have left this report for Nathanos before heading off on another mission.
QuestData.LogDescription: Recover the SI:7 Intel from Spymaster Knockwhistle in Blackbeak Overlook.
